      "section": [
        "Chin Village prison",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "Sokka and Katara, along with Mayor Tong, later revisited the prison to inform Aang of their discovery of evidence proving the Avatar's innocence. Tong, however, merely scoffed at the two for misunderstanding the village's court system, which did not permit the presentation of evidence. Aang remained in the prison until his trial the following day."
    },
    {
